# CSS Assignment 1

Yeh ek simple HTML + CSS assignment hai jisme maine alag–alag ## CSS formatting properties aur  ## colors ka use kiya hai.
Project ke files:

index.html – HTML structure
style.css – CSS styling
Features
Colors ka use kiya gaya hai (background, text, borders etc.)
Different CSS properties apply ki gayi hain (font, margin, padding, border, alignment etc.)
Clean aur structured HTML & CSS code
How to Run
Project download / clone karo.
index.html file ko browser mein open karo.
Learnings
Basic HTML structure samajhna
CSS ke alag–alag formatting properties apply karna
Color aur styling ka practical use
